<figureCitation captionStartId="F6404934" pageId="0" pageNumber="67134">a</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStartId="F6404935" pageId="0" pageNumber="67134">b</figureCitation>
). Dr. Erica McAlister, NHM, provided us with images of the holotype (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStartId="F6404929" pageId="0" pageNumber="67134">5</figureCitation>
<figureCitation captionStartId="F6404936" pageId="0" pageNumber="67134">c</figureCitation>
